<h2 class="font-display text-5xl font-bold text-[#E2E8F0]">How is it Formed?</h2>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-4">
<div class="bg-[#4A5568]/20 border border-[#4A5568]/40 rounded-xl p-5">
<p class="text-lg text-[#E2E8F0]/90 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Acid rain formation begins when <strong>sulfur dioxide (SO₂)</strong> and <strong>nitrogen oxides (NOₓ)</strong> are released into the atmosphere. These gases react with <span class="text-[#38B2AC] font-semibold">water vapor, oxygen, and other chemicals</span> to form mild solutions of sulfuric and nitric acid.
                    </p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="bg-[#1A202C]/60 border border-[#38B2AC]/30 rounded-lg p-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
<i class="fas fa-atom text-[#38B2AC] text-xl"></i>
<h4 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-[#E2E8F0]">Sulfur Dioxide Reaction</h4>
</div>
<div class="bg-[#2D3748] rounded-lg p-3 font-mono text-base text-center text-[#38B2AC]">
                                2SO₂ + O₂ + 2H₂O → 2H₂SO₄
                            </div>
<p class="text-sm text-[#E2E8F0]/70 mt-2">Sulfur dioxide + Oxygen + Water → Sulfuric acid</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-[#1A202C]/60 border border-[#38B2AC]/30 rounded-lg p-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
<i class="fas fa-atom text-[#38B2AC] text-xl"></i>
<h4 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-[#E2E8F0]">Nitrogen Oxide Reaction</h4>
</div>
<div class="bg-[#2D3748] rounded-lg p-3 font-mono text-base text-center text-[#38B2AC]">
                                2NO₂ + H₂O → HNO₂ + HNO₃
                            </div>
<p class="text-sm text-[#E2E8F0]/70 mt-2">Nitrogen dioxide + Water → Nitrous + Nitric acid</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 flex-1">
<div class="bg-[#38B2AC]/10 border border-[#38B2AC]/30 rounded-xl p-5 flex flex-col">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#38B2AC]/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
<span class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-[#38B2AC]">SO₂</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-[#E2E8F0]">Sulfur Dioxide</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-base text-[#E2E8F0]/80 leading-relaxed flex-1">
                            Comes mostly from <strong>burning coal</strong> in power plants and industrial facilities. Also produced by metal smelting and oil refining.
                        </p>
<div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-[#38B2AC]/20">
<p class="text-sm text-[#718096]"><i class="fas fa-industry mr-2"></i>Primary Source: Coal combustion</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-[#38B2AC]/10 border border-[#38B2AC]/30 rounded-xl p-5 flex flex-col">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#38B2AC]/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
<span class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-[#38B2AC]">NOₓ</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-[#E2E8F0]">Nitrogen Oxides</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-base text-[#E2E8F0]/80 leading-relaxed flex-1">
                            Mainly from <strong>car exhaust</strong> and automobile emissions. Also produced by power plants and industrial processes.
                        </p>
<div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-[#38B2AC]/20">
<p class="text-sm text-[#718096]"><i class="fas fa-car mr-2"></i>Primary Source: Vehicle emissions</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-[#4A5568]/20 border border-[#4A5568]/40 rounded-xl p-5 flex flex-col">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#38B2AC]/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
<i class="fas fa-ruler-vertical text-2xl text-[#38B2AC]"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-[#E2E8F0]">pH Scale</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-base text-[#E2E8F0]/80 leading-relaxed flex-1">
                            Measures how <strong>acidic or alkaline</strong> a liquid is. pH 7 is neutral. <span class="text-[#38B2AC] font-semibold">Lower numbers mean more acidic</span> and corrosive.
                        </p>
<div class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-[#4A5568]/40">
<p class="text-sm text-[#718096]"><i class="fas fa-info-circle mr-2"></i>Logarithmic scale: pH 4 is 10× more acidic than pH 5</p>
</div>
</div>
